        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="conclusion">
        <h2>10. Conclusion</h2>
        <p>UOS provides a unified operating system framework through ROSIX, supporting human-machine-physical collaboration. This whitepaper has enhanced technical details and industry use cases, and welcomes community feedback for further improvement.</p>
        <p>For more information, please visit：<a href="https://github.com/uos-projects/uos-rosix" target="_blank">https://github.com/uos-projects/uos-rosix</a></p>
      </section>
